    a4: 'Call (437) 524-1053 before 2 PM and we dispatch a technician to your Greektown address the same day, typically within 2-4 hours. We serve all Greektown streets including the Danforth Ave corridor, Logan Ave, Pape Ave, Woodbine Ave, Jones Ave, and Carlaw Ave. Our vans carry the gas igniter assemblies, drum belts, thermal fuses, and valve solenoid kits most commonly needed for Whirlpool, Maytag, and GE gas dryers. We also bring duct cleaning equipment to every Greektown call, since vent clearing is almost always part of the job. Most repairs in Greektown basement laundry rooms take 60-90 minutes. If a specialty part for an older model must be sourced, we return the next business day at no extra call-out charge. All work is backed by a 90-day parts and labour warranty. Mon-Fri 8am-8pm, Sat 9am-6pm, Sun 10am-5pm.',
